  "type": "mcq",
  "marks": 1,
  "readingTitle": "Misconception check",
  "reading": "<p><strong>❌ Common misconception:</strong> Writing a business plan means the business will definitely succeed.</p><p><strong>✅ The correct idea:</strong> A business plan reduces risk but cannot eliminate it. Always write 'reduces the risk of failure' — never say it 'guarantees success' or 'ensures the business will be profitable'.</p>",
