  "readingTitle": "Multiple Choice (1 mark) — Tricks with 'Place'",
  "reading": "<p>In multiple choice questions, examiners love testing your understanding of 'Place'.</p>\n      <p>Always remember: Place = <strong>Distribution Channels</strong>.</p>\n      <p>If you see options about factories, warehouses, or ordering raw materials, ignore them. Look for words like 'digital distribution', 'retailers', or 'wholesalers'.</p>",
