  "readingTitle": "Concept Link — Linking the Mix to the Target Market",
  "reading": "<p>When devising a marketing mix, it must always link back to the <strong>target market</strong> (from Unit 2.3).</p>\n      <p>If an exam scenario says the target market is 'low-income teenagers', every part of your suggested 4 Ps must match that demographic: low price, digital promotion (social media), modern design, and online/accessible place.</p>",
