  "readingTitle": "Evaluate (9 marks) — Creating a Marketing Mix",
  "reading": "<p>For high tariff questions, you may be asked to evaluate a proposed marketing mix or recommend one.</p>\n      <p>To score top marks, you must explicitly state how the parts of the mix <strong>work together</strong>. Don't just list a price and a promotion separately. Explain <em>why</em> that specific price supports that specific promotion method.</p>",
