  "reading": "<p>When evaluating if a business should use the PLC to plan marketing (like the Ford Motors 7-mark question), you must provide a balanced argument.</p>\n      <p><strong>Pro:</strong> Helps them know exactly when to spend money on advertising or when to reduce prices.</p>\n      <p><strong>Con:</strong> It ignores external factors. A competitor might release a revolutionary car, making Ford's car enter 'decline' years earlier than the graph predicted.</p>",
