  "source": "tips",
  "type": "mcq",
  "marks": 1,
  "readingTitle": "9-Mark Discuss Question — Discuss whether to change organisational structure (9 marks)",
  "reading": "For Beautiful Buds: K (define delayering) → U (explain the process) → APP x2 (use the NUMBERS: £600k + £700k saving, £300k extra supervisor costs, £200k redundancy) → AN x2 (show business impact of savings AND risks) → EVAL x3 (overall judgement with net saving of £1m per year, long-term vs short-term). ALWAYS use the specific figures provided.",
  "question": "For the 9-mark 'discuss whether to change organisational structure' question on Beautiful Buds, why is it important to use the specific figures (£600k, £700k, £300k, £200k)?",
