  "reading": "Analysis marks are only awarded for impacts on the BUSINESS — such as effects on revenue, profit, market share, costs, customer service, employee retention, reputation, or productivity. Writing 'employees will feel more motivated' scores as analysis. Writing 'better communication' does NOT — it just restates the question. Always push to the business consequence.",
