  "question": "Identify one method of selling products to customers. [1 mark]",
  "caseStudy": "Quality Textiles Ltd (QT) is a medium-sized, established business that manufactures clothes from its factory in Birmingham. Its clothes are sold to retail shops around the country.",
  "hint": "There are three main selling methods covered in this topic. Name just one — no explanation needed.",
