  "readingTitle": "Misconception check",
  "reading": "<p><strong>❌ Common misconception:</strong> Telesales is becoming irrelevant because of e-commerce.</p><p><strong>✅ The correct idea:</strong> Telesales remains important as a bridge between e-commerce and face-to-face selling, particularly for older customers, subscription renewals (insurance, utilities, phone contracts), and situations where customers want to negotiate directly.</p>",
  "question": "Is telesales becoming irrelevant because of e-commerce?",
