  "marks": 1,
  "readingTitle": "Misconception check",
  "reading": "<p><strong>❌ Common misconception:</strong> Students think 'the high street' is the only location option for a business.</p><p><strong>✅ The correct idea:</strong> Businesses can locate anywhere — high streets, industrial estates, online warehouses, near ports, in enterprise zones. The best location depends entirely on the type of business and which factors are most important to it.</p>",
