  "starter": "Break-even formula = FC ÷ (SP − VC) (K)\nContribution = £30 − £5 = £25 per session (APP)\nBreak-even = £6,000 ÷ £25 = ... sessions (APP)\nAnswer: ... sessions (AN)",
