  "caseStudy": "An extract from Pia's Diner's cash flow forecast for July is shown below.<table class=\"case-table\"><caption>Pia's Diner — July Extract</caption><tr><th></th><th>July £</th></tr><tr><td>Total inflow</td><td>?</td></tr><tr><td>Total outflow</td><td>13,500</td></tr><tr><td>Net cash flow</td><td>−1,900</td></tr><tr><td>Opening balance</td><td>−2,300</td></tr><tr><td>Closing balance</td><td>−4,200</td></tr></table>",
