  "pageId": "6-2-the-economic-climate",
  "pageName": "6.2 The Economic Climate",
  "source": "tf",
  "type": "tf",
  "marks": 1,
  "question": "Aldi's rapid growth after 2008 was partly due to the poor economic climate.",
